                            <comment id="16737662" author="mshuler" created="Tue, 8 Jan 2019 23:52:16 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nobr&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/attachment/12954240/12954240_0001-Update-downloads-for-sha256-sha512-checksum-files.patch&quot; title=&quot;0001-Update-downloads-for-sha256-sha512-checksum-files.patch attached to CASSANDRA-14970&quot;&gt;0001-Update-downloads-for-sha256-sha512-checksum-files.patch&lt;sup&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rendericon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/link_attachment_7.gif&quot; height=&quot;7&quot; width=&quot;7&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&#160;attached for the cassandra-builds repo - download the new checksum files for release publication.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
